boat.name: Cyrus V
boat.short_description: Cyrus V is a fold-up dinghy built by Seahopper Ltd. She is new as at January 2022, and has yet to be sailed as a change in circumstances has precluded this. She will make a fine, storable tender for a cruiing boat. When not in use she is stored in purpose built shower proof bags. She was intended for sailing on inland waters or estuaries.
